<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta content='text/html; charset=UTF-8' http-equiv='Content-Type' />
    <style>
      body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; }
      .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; }
      .header { background-color: #F59E0B; color: white; padding: 20px; text-align: center; }
      .content { background-color: #f9fafb; padding: 30px; }
      .review-box { background-color: white; padding: 20px; margin: 20px 0; border-left: 4px solid #F59E0B; }
      .button { display: inline-block; padding: 12px 24px; background-color: #4F46E5; color: white; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 6px; margin-top: 20px; }
      .footer { text-align: center; padding: 20px; color: #6b7280; font-size: 14px; }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="header">
        <h1>âš  Review Under Moderation</h1>
      </div>
      
      <div class="content">
        <h2>Hello <%= @user.email.split('@').first.capitalize %>,</h2>
        
        <p>Your review of <strong><%= @game.title %></strong> has been flagged for moderation review by our community or moderators.</p>
        
        <div class="review-box">
          <h3><%= @review.title %></h3>
          <p><%= truncate(@review.body, length: 200) %></p>
        </div>
        
        <p>Our moderation team will review your content to ensure it complies with our community guidelines. This is a standard process and doesn't necessarily mean your review violated any rules.</p>
        
        <p>If your review is found to comply with our guidelines, it will be approved and published. Otherwise, we may contact you with specific feedback.</p>
        
        <a href="<%= @guidelines_url %>" class="button">Review Community Guidelines</a>
      </div>
      
      <div class="footer">
        <p>&copy; <%= Time.current.year %> GamesReview.com. All rights reserved.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
